{
  "stem": "2165.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- the youngest daughter was probably about three years older than me, and then-- then the sons were probably five and six, seven and 10 years older than me, yes.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "School was not allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, when the Germans came, my uncle tried still to put me in underground, in cheder, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very dangerous if they caught you, so my cousins persuaded him that that's enough.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And but it only lasted a few months, then it became illegal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No schooling.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, Jews were not allowed to go to any school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we lived-- since my mother was taken, we lived there till the end, till we were taken to the-- to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was from 1941 till around December 1942, they opened the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, mostly yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes the sons disappeared to work in a certain area, but then they showed up again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Matter of fact, one of my-- one of her sons, which was my cousin, organized a-- a little group, a partisan group.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went to the woods, and they tried to do this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they showed up because their parents were there and their brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were together, living in-- in the ghetto in two little rooms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in 1943-- in 1943, around May-- they declared Judenfrei, which is--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which you probably know about Judenfrei.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had a bunker under the floor, in a basement in the same building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were prepared, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto, we had the little--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If-- if i can-- if I remember before the ghetto, when I lived with my uncle and aunt, that was also in the basement.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, you see, the Germans used to have what they call actions.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
